KrR-Fh4_-7s.title: 8 minutes of Rob Anderson's best bits 2021 | heartthrobert heartthrobanderson
KrR-Fh4_-7s.author: Rob Anderson
KrR-Fh4_-7s.description:
A compilation of my best videos from instagram and tiktok in 2021: Gays over Covid, Don't Wake Sugar Daddy, What I think happens after I hang out with new people, YouTube Chiropractors, Making a bath for my gay son, Jessie J singing Price Tag but it's a Shark Tank pitch, White gay men thinking they're a double minority, and Fergie's Star Spangled banner as a children's book.

More FartThrob on the internet:
TikTok: Heartthrobert https://www.tiktok.com/@heartthrobert

Twitter: smartthrob https://twitter.com/smartthrob
